{
  "stem": "11205.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- my parents-- I-- because I need a profession, my parents sent me-- it was the last few weeks, I think, to a friend-- to their friend-- to learn some sewing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I liked it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Being-- coming from a family, you know, where it was-- there, I couldn't even hold the needles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why they sent me to a friend of-- of my parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had what I remember, one uncle, my mother's brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Adam.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Adam Pomp.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had my-- from my father-- on my father's side, he still had parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They lived-- they lived in [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Grabowiec. ?] That's quite-- quite far, and it's a very little place, and I went-- only once I went to visit them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my-- it was school holiday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My parents send me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went there by coach, and you travel, I don't remember, from 4 o'clock in the afternoon till 7:00 in the morning, and you have to go through-- through a forest.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one ride, I remember, and the horse knew already because he used to come pick up some goods for-- for shops, and the horse-- the-- the man fell asleep, and I was sitting on there, and in the forest, I was so scared, I used to wake him up.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, sleep, sleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, that was the first time I went away from my home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was maybe eight, nine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sent me there to say for all the vacation, school holidays.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I couldn't-- after three days, I came back, and I-- I-- I was-- so I missed so much, the family, so I never-- I never went without my family.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the first time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
